# The Tactile Wanderer Design System

## Creative North Star
"The Digital Field Journal" — premium linen-bound journal aesthetic. Editorial layouts, asymmetric breathing room, organic warmth. NOT a utility spreadsheet.

## Strict Rules (never violate)

### No-Line Rule
Never use `border` or `border-b` for sectioning. Use background color shifts (different surface tiers) or negative space instead.

### No-Black Rule
Never use `#000000`, `black`, or `text-black`. All dark text uses `text-on-surface` (#1b1c1c) or `text-on-surface-variant`.

### No-Sharp-Corners Rule
Every interactive element (buttons, inputs, cards, modals) uses at least `rounded-xl` (0.75rem). Chips use `rounded-full`.

### No-Dividers Rule
Never use `<hr>` or `border-b` between list items. Increase spacing (`gap-3` -> `gap-4`) instead.

### Secondary = CTA Only
`bg-secondary` and `text-secondary` are reserved for actionable CTAs ("Book Now", "Add Trip", primary action buttons). Never use for decoration, section headings, or informational content.

### Tonal Elevation
Depth from surface color contrast, not shadows. Layer: surface -> surface-container-low -> surface-container -> surface-container-high.
Shadows only for floating elements: `shadow-ambient` (32px blur, 8px Y, 4% opacity).

### Glassmorphism for Floating Elements
Nav bars and overlays: `bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-[20px]`.

## Color Token Usage
```
bg-surface                   base page
bg-surface-container-lowest  lifted cards
bg-surface-container-low     content areas
bg-surface-container         mid containers
bg-surface-container-high    input backgrounds
bg-surface-container-highest inactive chips
text-on-surface              primary text
text-on-surface-variant      muted/secondary text
bg-primary                   primary actions (non-CTA)
bg-secondary                 CTA buttons only
bg-secondary-fixed           active chips
border-outline-variant/15    ghost borders (15% opacity)
```

## Typography
- `font-headline` (Epilogue): display text, destination names, page titles
- `font-body` (Manrope): body text, descriptions
- `font-label` (Manrope): metadata, dates, prices — use `tracking-[0.05rem]`

## Component Patterns

### Primary Buttons (non-CTA)
```
rounded-xl px-6 py-3 font-body font-medium
bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-container
text-on-primary
hover:from-primary-container hover:to-primary transition-all
active:scale-[0.98]
```

### CTA Buttons
```
rounded-xl px-6 py-3 font-body font-medium
bg-secondary text-on-secondary
hover:opacity-90 active:scale-[0.98]
```

### Cards
```
bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl p-4 shadow-card
```
No borders, no dividers inside.

### Input Fields
```
bg-surface-container-high rounded-xl px-4 py-3
focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-fixed/50 focus:outline-none
text-on-surface placeholder:text-on-surface-variant
```
No border on default state. Ghost border at 15% if needed: `border border-outline-variant/15`.

### Selection Chips
```
rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 font-label text-sm
inactive: bg-surface-container-highest text-on-surface-variant
active:   bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed
```

### Floating Navigation
```
fixed bottom-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2
bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-[20px]
rounded-xl shadow-ambient
px-6 py-3 flex gap-6
```
